4170,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:53:15.000Z","msg":"講下 Electrical Engineering 必揀既 Elective courses (48 credits)<br />\n <br />\nGroup I 選擇: <br />\n<br />\n1. MECH3407 Advanced partial differential equations &amp; complex variables <br />\n呢科比 2407 好 grade 好多，2407 B -&gt; 3407 A<br />\n<br />\n✓ ELEC3846 Numerical methods and optimisation<br />\n淺到就算成個 sem 唔上堂，肯溫 3 日書就穩 B <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGroup A 選擇: <br />\n<br />\n✓ ELEC4145 Building services - electrical services<br />\n✓ ELEC4146 Building services - electrical installations<br />\n<br />\n搵工必讀，consultant 公司 interview 必問呢兩科既內容<br />\n<br />\n✓ ELEC4147 Power system analysis and control<br />\n✓ ELEC4142 Power system protection and switchgear<br />\n✓ ELEC4141 Electric railway systems<br />\n<br />\nY Hou 老師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔洗上堂剩操 PP，必 take 穩 A<br />\n<br />\n✓ ELEC4148 Smart grid and renewable energy systems<br />\n<br />\nJ Zhong 老師 同 Hou 老師一樣咁好，電機女神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n✗ ELEC4144 Electric vehicle technology<br />\n千萬不要系列 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Chur 爆又唔好 grade <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cb363f523e37aab3c7430af9422d9e78a2d1dd","tid":775463,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ec6cef6ea1dcf0c3623d38f3c87b59fada3a7dc1","tid":775463,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:51:37.000Z","msg":"嚟緊ocamp會唔會見到你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:53:36.000Z","msg":"返工做狗呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968dbe89de906acdd169e108f6e0429bfd5fa48e","tid":775463,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53211453bb07d8ea921863ede9b5c6f7a4f7659c","tid":775463,"uid":120462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c